This is GNU Guile-OpenGL, an OpenGL interface for GNU Guile.  See
http://www.gnu.org/project/guile/ for more on Guile.

Guile-OpenGL is available under the GNU Lesser General Public License,
either version 3 or, at your option, any later version.  See LICENSE for
all details.

Note that for any copyright year range specified as YYYY-ZZZZ in this
package, the range specifies every single year in that closed interval.

Guile-OpenGL requires Guile version 2.0.0 or later.

To use Guile-OpenGL without installing it, use the "env" script that is
created in the top of the build directory.

Guile-OpenGL has a complete manual.  Once you install it, you can read
it via "info guile-opengl", or even just "info gl".  It is also
available in other forms; see
http://www.gnu.org/project/guile-opengl/manual/ for details.

To contribute to Guile-OpenGL, check out the source code from git:

  git clone git://git.sv.gnu.org/guile-opengl.git

See https://savannah.gnu.org/projects/guile-opengl/ for more details

Please send problem reports to <bug-guile@gnu.org>.  Discussion of
Guile-OpenGL takes place at <guile-user@gnu.org>.
